title: Miss Alana Murphy
text: Car lab is perfect to deal with. Watch out on the extras which the rental company try to hit you with. Make sure you understand them fully before signing up to them. The extra insurance can often be insured separately for the year, as many rentals as you need for the same price as a one off extra insurance charge
